fields.name: Switchgear & Controls
fields.heading: Switchgear & Control
fields.description:
ANWAR AL MEIHA MODERN LLC, specializes in design & manufacture of customized quality low voltage switchgear & control panel boards of various capacity to suit water, electricity, infrastructure, private buildings, commercial buildings and utility projects under the brand name of SAFELINE.

The company is the recognized panel builder for ABB and authorized panel builder for L&T switchgear components which are both a known leader in power & automation technologies.

The switchgear division started its operations in 2018 and is a well-known and leading switchgear panel builder in the region which is spread across a 1500 sqm factory and a well dedicated team of qualified professionals with modern manufacturing & assembling facilities with latest machineries & best-known testing equipments.
fields.description_two:
The team is qualified and backed up with principles, regular audits, strict design, manufacturing standards and stringent quality control with specialized inventory control. The company manufactures products complying IEC 61439 – 1&2, BS EN 61439-1, OES 4, 7, 22 and other relevant standards.

All products manufactured at our factory undergo a systematic process of inspection at each stage right from receiving the materials and are covered by our warranty against manufacturing or operation defects for a period of 18months from the date of delivery or 12 months from the date of commissioning whichever is earlier.
fields.sub_content: We are striving to enhance our strategy and technology awareness in order to be in line with the requirement of the market and provide the best solutions to our clients with secure, safe and reliable products.
